channel.title: Your best high?
channel.description:
okay guys so im high right now, and im not trying to brag or anything as if its a scheme to seem cool. im definitely not. i just got to thinking, (im sure alot of you are recreational drug users and i get that) maybe everyone could try to define their best high. i personally have strange highs, im totally gone in the head and feel minor body pain, like sensitive nerves etc.
ps just a topic for highness gl post best high best high chosen by myself to win the reward wins high of the month badge gl
